author_ssm: University Archives Staff.  Inventory updated by Margaret Fraser and Samantha Gibson, September 2010.
unittitle_ssm: RISM Conference Papers: Cross-Cultural Perspectives on Cannabis
abstract_ssm: The August 1973 Cross-Cultural Perspectives on Cannabis Conference convened in Chicago, Illinois.  The Conference was part of the Ninth International Congress of the International Union of Anthropological and Ethnological Sciences. The RISM Conference Papers: Cross-Cultural Perspectives on Cannabis documents the planning of the 1973 Cross-Cultural Perspectives on Cannabis Conference and the process between 1973 and 1975 to publish a volume of papers that were presented by its attendees.
